        public boolean hasActiveDependencies​(heros.solver.Pair<soot.SootMethod,​D> abstraction)
        Description copied from interface: IGarbageCollectorPeer
        Checks whether the given abstraction has any open dependencies in any of the solvers that are members of this peer group that prevent its jump functions from being garbage collected
        Parameters:
        abstraction - The abstraction to check
        Returns:
        True if the abstraction has active dependencies and thus cannot be garbage-collected, false otherwise
